2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b409c892923e112c516b4679a8ceb1fcb93a21d1","tid":638642,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"都好嘅，寧願新加坡搶左香港個味都唔想支那搶走個名"},{"pid":"b3a63fafed474b3096c6b6cf168d7da2cb264163","tid":638642,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T12:51:57.000Z","msg":"中國或成為最大的贏家"}]}